description:
We've come to the end of a very long road my friends. The end of a scary and jumpscare-filled road, but an amazing road nonetheless. I (for some reason) never though this day would come, but we've come to the end of Five Nights At Freddy's, and to Scott to YOU we all say: Thank you.
